<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Product Description</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding:4px;
      background-image: linear-gradient(120deg, #c9f0c0, #7ff572); /* light yellow gradient */

      /* background-color:rgb(186, 217, 186); light green background */
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .blog-post {
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0,0.1);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .blog-post img {
      width: 250px;
      height: 250px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-right: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0); /* adding shadow to image */
      margin-bottom: 20px; /* adding margin to image */
    }

    .blog-post .details {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .blog-post .details h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    .blog-post .details p {
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .blog-post .description {
      flex: 1;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .blog-post .description h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    .blog-post .description p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #666;
    }

    .order-now {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #dc2626;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .order-now:hover {
      background-color: #c41e1e; /* Darker red on hover */
    }

    .experience {
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .experience h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    .experience p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #666;
    }

    .experience input[type="text"] {
      width: calc(100% - 22px); /* Adjusted width to account for border */
      padding: 10px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 6px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .experience input[type="submit"] {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #dc2626;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: 20px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .experience input[type="submit"]:hover {
      background-color: #c41e1e; /* Darker red on hover */
    }

    /* Customer Review Boxes */
    .customer-review {
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0,0.1);
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .customer-review h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    .customer-review p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="blog-post">
      <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/002/932/069/non_2x/raw-coffee-beans-rgb-color-icon-unprocessed-arabica-unroasted-robusta-seeds-plant-with-coffee-fruit-crop-on-stem-isolated-illustration-barista-accessories-simple-filled-line-drawing-vector.jpg" alt="Product Image">
      <div class="details">
        <h2>Product Title</h2>
        <p>Company: Company Name</p>
        <p>Price: $XX.XX</p>
        <p>Type: Product Type</p>
        <p>Likes: 100</p>
        <p>Purchases: 50</p>
        <a href="#" class="order-now">Order Now</a>
      </div>
      <div class="description">
        <h3>Product Description</h3>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus ac enim vitae purus rhoncus mattis. Donec id volutpat eros. Quisque fringilla massa ut risus accumsan, ac laoreet tortor suscipit.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="experience">
      <h2>Share Your Experience</h2>
      <p>Sharing your experiences can be incredibly valuable for both yourself and others. When you share your experiences, you not only reflect on your own journey but also provide insights, advice, and encouragement to those who may be going through similar situations. Your experiences have the power to inspire, educate, and empower others.</p>
      <form action="#">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Share your experience...">
        <input type="submit" value="Submit">
      </form>
    </div>

    <!-- Customer Review Boxes -->
    <div class="customer-review">
      <h3>Customer Review</h3>
      <p>I recently purchased this product and I'm extremely satisfied with it. The quality is excellent, and it exceeded my expectations. The design is sleek and modern, and it fits perfectly with my needs. Additionally, the customer service was outstanding; they were responsive and helpful throughout the entire purchasing process. I highly recommend this product to anyone looking for a reliable solution.</p>
    </div>


</body>
</html>
